software.leonov.util.gson

Class OptionalTypeAdapter<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gson.TypeAdapter<Optional<E>>
      • software.leonov.util.gson.OptionalTypeAdapter<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of the element contained within the Optional

    public final class OptionalTypeAdapter<E>
extends TypeAdapter<Optional<E>>
    A TypeAdapter which can serialize and deserialize of Optional values to and from JSON.

    Empty Optionals are serialized as JSON-encoded NULLs while present values are serialized using an adapter obtained from the provided Gson instance.

        Constructs a new OptionalTypeAdapter.

        While this constructor can be invoked manually, it will most commonly be invoked by OptionalTypeAdapterFactory, which in turn will be registered with the provided Gson instance.

        Parameters:
        gson - a Gson instance which can handle the serialization and deserialization of the type of element contained within the Optional
